Caren Lyn Tackett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caren_Lyn_Tackett 0 Caren Lyn Tackett (née Manuel; born August 14, 1976) is an American stage actress who has provided voice-overs for animation productions of 4Kids Entertainment, including Winx Club, Pokémon Chronicles and Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles.
